creator: Kinzoo Technologies Inc.
descriptionHtml:
Kinzoo Studio lets you create your own characters and stories—and easily turn them into videos you can share. Dress your characters in millions of outfit combinations, take them to far-away locations and easily stitch your scenes together.

CREATE YOUR OWN CHARACTERS & STORIES

* Build your own custom avatars to use in your stories

* Millions of character combinations: choose different outfits, hairstyles, skin tones and expressions

* Explore dozens of different locations: set your stories inside, outside, near or far

* Turn your stories into videos: easily export your creations so you can share with family and friends

EXPLORE THE MALL

* Discover clothes for every style: find hundreds of t-shirts, sweaters, jackets, pants, shorts, shoes—and more

* Travel to far-away places: take your stories somewhere new with over 60 different backgrounds

* Adopt different pets: visit the pet adoption center and give your characters a new best friend

ANIMATE YOUR ADVENTURE AND SHARE VIDEOS

* Create scenes and stitch them together: tell your story by putting it together in a video

* Export your stories: save your stories as mp4 video files to easily share them in Kinzoo Messenger, on YouTube or any other video-sharing platform

* Access your stories on any device: save your stories in Kinzoo Studio and edit them from anywhere
descriptionShort: Create characters and stories—and easily turn them into videos you can share.
